 	<div id="main-article-info">
 		
					
				
			<h1
																									>The good news is that a Smoker's Permit will cost only &pound;10. The bad news is how you apply for it</h1>
				
					<p id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"																				>You still have freedom of choice. Provided you're carrying a valid Freedom  of Choice Permit</p>
		
				
