 			<div class="section">
				<h1>The good news is that a Smoker's Permit will cost only &pound;10. The bad news is how you apply for it</h1>
		   		    			    									   	This article appeared  on p5 of the <a href=http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2008/feb/18/g2  >G2</a> section of 					   	<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian"  >the Guardian</a>
					   	on <time datetime="2008-02-18" pubdate><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2008/feb/18">Monday 18 February 2008</a></time>.
					   	It was published on
							<a href='http://www.guardian.co.uk/'>guardian.co.uk</a>
							at <time datetime="2008-02-18T00:00GMT" pubdate>09.28 GMT on Monday 18 February 2008</time>.
					   	
						 It was first published at <time datetime="2008-02-18T00:03">00.03 GMT on Monday 18 February 2008</time>. 				   								</div>
