<img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2010/08/23/CliffordChallenger/5ae38b0a-526e-47a5-b9e5-6b97c3c06796/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/discussion/user/CliffordChallenger" title="User profile page">CliffordChallenger</a>

                            
